Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • PayrollProcessing.Employee
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Fulltime, Parttime
    public class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
    The Employee class used to hold the profile of an employee and the payment. Provides access to changing the payment of an employee.
